e_name": "Art-08.png", "id": "1891902310961288", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75196225_1891902314294621_2238078460830108184_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=lkO7Ut2GQGsQ7kNvgHlepCd&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Ap8EOQ_nbJbgYZHiTjYKNm6&oh=00_AYCEUjSIe-ThSHELDBvV4Y282vSyf7B2yUNBmRl2dt4x2Q&oe=66D82F07"}, {"file_name": "Art-08.png", "id": "782210065728523", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974769_782210069061856_6175752411345744086_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=PIbkI_cTIMsQ7kNvgFm2z-e&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Ap8EOQ_nbJbgYZHiTjYKNm6&oh=00_AYAMjZdboZCyTyGik1duqY2EII2NqrOrrhfxs2W8nSloAQ&oe=66D831F8"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Art-08.png", "id": "423398472215020", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974891_423398475548353_5249155989052516159_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=145VLMkAzZkQ7kNvgH-vPh1&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Ap8EOQ_nbJbgYZHiTjYKNm6&oh=00_AYBJBZ5kVJ_oeco0DXF3HiQn_iXTQYX1WhqiOeNbcer2MA&oe=66D83446"}, "display_name": "Touchy Feely", "keywords": [], "long_description": "This is the first draft of a system I want to use to build experiences with hand tracking, it features\n\n - touch response, this is colour and sound for temperature and pressure\n - custom shader, I'm learning shader graph and want to make a battered comic book style\n\nWhat I hope to do\n\n - create a small short story in this space, about someone packing down the apartment of a loved one that has passed away.\n - polish the grab and feedback mechanics based on some feedback\n - add teleport and explore hand based teleport\n - work on more natural engaging interactions\n\nI'm making this public to get a read on the grabbing and the art style, I still want to add audio and polish the mechanics. My goal is also to create technical and creative experiments and share them. I want to publish often and develop in 